{"tid":1460082,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[文宣組請入]班中產經過咗811事件之後嘅改變","createTime":"2019-08-13T01:11:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T01:47:51.000Z","uid":286552,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"29cec78b46b22d7236687a94c3970ec2addc0980","tid":1460082,"uid":286552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T01:11:53.000Z","msg":"我份job就係喺做餐廳waiter啦，我嗰間係做中產生意，我原本打算收工之後去機場嘅，但係點知就到6點嘅時候你哋話機場要散水就無去到，但係我做lunch嘅時候係咁聽到班中產係咁討論811，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">尤其是係女first aid被射爆眼同埋係葵芳放煙</span></span>，佢哋話<span style=\"font-size: large;\"></span><span style=\"color: red;\">無輪班示威者做咗d咩都唔應該係地鐵站放煙，</span><span style=\"font-size: large;\"></span><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">更何況係瞄頭開槍。</span></span>其他事件反而無咩點特別提到(嗰時佢哋好似唔係好知機場有集會)。今次連平時都係藍嘅熟客都係到屌鳩班黑警，話要清場都有好多方法。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">啫係話我哋唔單止要煲大721，仲要</span><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不停放大班死黑警係811所做嘅一切事件，尤其係被射爆眼同地鐵站放催淚彈，</span></span>我哋就能夠拉到更多中產嘅支持，民意就會更加企係我哋呢面。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">所以唔該咁多位文宣組，煲大811事件<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港，時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"578f5a9b38fd77aad2bf9cf11c2b81650283568c","tid":1460082,"uid":286552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T01:12:21.000Z","msg":"光"},{"pid":"9649d3292cfd15036f8df3e88bb15f57c9fb19b2","tid":1460082,"uid":286552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T01:12:31.000Z","msg":"復"},{"pid":"8bce22c837ffb0764c2b31f9644c062c96fba612","tid":1460082,"uid":286552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T01:12:41.000Z","msg":"香"},{"pid":"445e2752711f453006cbd977a5a193c5639f62b1","tid":